.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Collective monetary field in the \fBChiffres\fP system\&. 

\fBEther\fP represents the "atmosphere" of value shared by all \fBChiffres\fP\&. It reacts to individual gains and losses, and in turn influences the probability space of all future mutations\&.

.PP
Core principles:
.IP "\(bu" 2
When a wallet gains in rest, \fBEther\fP is "consumed" → density decreases, value of all \fBChiffres\fP increases slightly (rarer field)\&.
.IP "\(bu" 2
When a wallet loses in rest, \fBEther\fP "dissolves" → density increases; The value of all \fBChiffres\fP decreases slightly (thicker field)\&.
.PP

.PP
\fBEther\fP acts as a global coupling mechanism: no mutation is purely individual\&. The system becomes organically self-regulating\&. 
